The paper is about the capacity limits of graph neural networks, which is a topic closely related to machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves optimization and estimation problems, which are related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper uses theoretical computer science techniques, which could also place it in the cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) sub-category.
